# .forceignore v2
.forceignore
**/jsconfig.json
**/.eslintrc.json
**/lwc/**/__tests__/**

# CLI parsing issue with folder metadata in source format
**/reportFolders/Advertising_Analytics.reportFolder-meta.xml
**/dashboardFolders/Advertising_Analytics.dashboardFolder-meta.xml
**/dashboardFolders/MediaCloud.dashboardFolder-meta.xml

# Unexpected child metadata — quick action inside CustomObject directory
**/objects/Account/quickActions/Link_Agency.quickAction-meta.xml

# Reports — invalid elements for this org's API version
**/reports/Advertising_Analytics/*.report-meta.xml
**/reportTypes/Period_Snapshot_Forecast_Accuracy.reportType-meta.xml

# Flow-type quick actions not supported in this org
**/quickActions/New_Advertiser.quickAction-meta.xml
**/quickActions/New_Agency.quickAction-meta.xml

# Flows using flowruntime:lookupField or recordChoiceSets not available in this org
**/flows/Link_Agency_To_Advertiser.flow-meta.xml
**/flows/Retire_Category_With_Successor.flow-meta.xml

# FlexiPage / App using schema elements not valid in this org type
**/flexipages/MDM_Workspace_Home.flexipage-meta.xml
**/flexipages/Agency_Account_Record_Page.flexipage-meta.xml
**/applications/MDM_Workspace.app-meta.xml

# Named Credential — type element invalid in this org
**/namedCredentials/Matrix_API.namedCredential-meta.xml

# Custom Metadata Type object — deploymentStatus not allowed
**/objects/Revenue_Code_Mapping__mdt.object-meta.xml

# Custom Tabs — object element invalid in CustomTab
**/tabs/Inbound_Staging__c.tab-meta.xml
**/tabs/Load_Batch__c.tab-meta.xml
**/tabs/Mapping_Rule__c.tab-meta.xml
**/tabs/Source_System__c.tab-meta.xml

# Dashboards — expandOtherItems invalid in DashboardComponent
**/dashboards/Advertising_Analytics/Weekly_Analytics_Dashboard.dashboard-meta.xml
**/dashboards/MediaCloud/Sales_Manager_Dashboard.dashboard-meta.xml

# Flows — screens element contiguity / unsupported lookupField extension
**/flows/Create_Agency_Account.flow-meta.xml
**/flows/Create_Direct_Buy_Advertiser.flow-meta.xml
**/flows/Makegood_Or_Cancellation.flow-meta.xml
**/flows/Traffic_Copy_Entry.flow-meta.xml
**/flows/Pitch_Project_Creator.flow-meta.xml

# Field type change blocked by existing org data
**/objects/Actual_Revenue__c/fields/Revenue_Type__c.field-meta.xml

# Custom Metadata Type — object-level file (subdir pattern)
**/objects/Revenue_Code_Mapping__mdt/Revenue_Code_Mapping__mdt.object-meta.xml

# LWC — API v62 literal expression incompatibility or missing @api property
**/lwc/fileUploadSource
**/lwc/sourceFileUpload
**/lwc/pitchProjectCreator

# LWC already deployed with correct lightning__FlowScreen target; redeploy triggers false conflict
**/lwc/periodCloseActions

# Filename-only fallbacks for files that exist on this branch — ** patterns can be unreliable
# when the file physically exists in the source tree (SF CLI v2 forceignore limitation)
New_Advertiser.quickAction-meta.xml
New_Agency.quickAction-meta.xml
Create_Agency_Account.flow-meta.xml
Create_Direct_Buy_Advertiser.flow-meta.xml
Link_Agency_To_Advertiser.flow-meta.xml
